sri lanka to uproot or bud disea rubber tree sri lanka will uproot rubber tree that are more than two year old and affect by the leaf disea corynespora , the head of the govern 's rubber research institut told reuter . rodney de mel said affect tree less than two year old would undergo base-bud -- attach a clone as close as possibl to the trunk 's base and cut off the top of the tree onc the bud ha taken . uproot or base-bud tree matur later , cau an output loss estim at 350 kilo per hectar from the sixth year when they begin produc . about 7,000 acr are plant with the high yield ric 103 varieti , the clone afflict by corynespora . onli about 2,000 acr are affect by the disea , which cau leav to fall off , de mel said . sri lanka ha 508,000 acr plant with rubber tree . de mel said the disea wa detect in nurseri as earli as in middl 1985 , but it wa onli in august-septemb 1986 that it becam widespread . the institut is conduct a survey to determin how mani tree will be uproot or base-bud . healthi tree will be spray and remain under observ . t.p . lilaratn , head of the govern 's rubber control depart , which monitor the industri , told reuter replant and base-bud would have to be undertaken befor late may when the monsoon rain begin . de mel said clone in the nurseri which are suscept to corynespora , identifi as ric 103 , ric 52 , ric 104 , ric 106 , ric 107 and ric 118 , will be uproot and burn . the same procedur will be undertaken for the foreign clone indentifi as nab 12 , rrim 725 , fx25 , ppn 2444 , ppn 2447 , kr 21 and ppn 2058. lilaratn said the suscept clone would be replac by pb 86 , rrim 600 , rric 110 , rric 121 , ric 100 and ric 102. these six varieti would also be use to replac tree uproot or base-bud , de mel said . lilaratn said planter would receiv 10,000 rupe per hectar for replant and plant would be free of charg . `` but no compen is contempl at the moment , `` he ad . de mel said a drought in sri lanka ha help control the spread of the disea . `` the drought ha not stop the disea , but probabl help in some way becau tree have not been affect in area that are dri , `` he said . broker said the disea had not affect price becau it ha not cau a drop in product . price for the best latex crepe at the colombo auction last week firm to 20.19 rupe per kilo from 20.05 rupe at the previou sale .